tellraw @s[scores={LANGUAGE=1}] {"text":"°-° Jack Arrow : ","color":"green","extra":[{"text":"Indeed, this map only indicates one of our previous hideouts, it won't be of any utility. However, I have informations that will spark your interest. There is an island on south of Asunark! It's a lair filled to the brim with former soldiers converted to ship scuttling. Yes, they are in a way our competitors, but more than that they are also led by a completely crazy captain and hide an incredible treasure in the ruins of the island. Before you rush in, know that there is a secret entry. Unfortunately I went there and it's closed by a huge lock. But I know one of their ships stranded deeply at extreme south from here on the coast. It could contain the key. Anyway, if you have an interest in their treasure, go to the wreck to find a huge key, sneak in their lair on the island and get rid of their captain...","color":"dark_aqua"}]}